metadata.description:
This token is verifiable for admission to VeeCon 2024

This token is a collectible that lives on the Ethereum blockchain

This a G.O.O. (Gary Originally Owned) VeeFriends token, which was minted in May 2021 as part of the VeeFriends Series 1 inaugural launch. Out of the 10,255 VeeFriends Series 1 supply, Gary Vaynerchuk held back 1,242 tokens from the public auction for his private collection. G.O.O. VeeFriends tokens will forever have special significance with GaryVee as the original owner and their unique G.O.O. badge signifier.
